### Performance Strategies

- Static Site Generation (SSG) -- entire site pre-rendered at build time
- Only Section 0 (Ganesha) loads on initial paint. Remaining sections lazy-loaded
- All images use next/image with automatic WebP/AVIF conversion
- Gallery images load only when gallery section entered (Intersection Observer)
- Fonts: subset to used characters only (Hindi + English glyphs)
- CSS animations preferred over JS where possible (petals, shimmer)
- Framer Motion: tree-shake unused features
- Audio file loaded only after first user interaction
- No external tracking scripts on initial load

