## RESPONSIVE DESIGN

### Breakpoints

| Name | Range | Layout Notes | Mobile S | 320-374px | Compact spacing, smaller fonts, 1-col gallery |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Mobile M | 375-424px | Primary mobile target, all features work here | Mobile L | 425-767px | Slightly more breathing room |
| Tablet | 768-1023px | 2-col gallery, wider event cards | Desktop | 1024px+ | Max-width 800px container, progress dots visible |

### Mobile-First Rules

- Design mobile-first, enhance for larger screens
- Touch targets minimum 48x48px
- No hover-dependent functionality (hover is enhancement only)
- Swipe gestures: optional enhancement for section navigation
- Palace door transition: 3D on desktop, golden fade on mobile (performance)
- Gallery: 1 column mobile, 2 columns tablet+
- Event cards: full-width stack on mobile
- Floating nav: bottom-right on mobile, top-right on desktop
- Progress dots: desktop only

