## ACCESSIBILITY (WCAG 2.1 AA)

### Color Contrast

| Pair | Ratio | Status | Cream (#D4CFC5) on Midnight (#0A1628) | 11.2:1 | AAA Pass |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Gold (#C9A96E) on Midnight (#0A1628) | 6.8:1 | AA Pass | Midnight (#0A1628) on Gold (#C9A96E) | 6.8:1 | AA Pass (primary button) |
| Muted (#8B7340) on Midnight (#0A1628) | 4.0:1 | AA Pass (large text only) |  |  |  |

### Motion & Animations

- All animations respect prefers-reduced-motion media query
- Reduced motion: all transitions become simple 0.3s cross-fade
- Reduced motion: floating petals hidden entirely
- Reduced motion: shimmer effects become static gold
- Reduced motion: countdown uses simple number swap, no flip
- No auto-playing video or flashing content

### Keyboard & Screen Reader

- Full keyboard navigation through all sections and interactive elements
- Logical tab order follows visual flow (Section 0 through 5)
- All buttons have descriptive aria-labels
- Decorative elements (petals, dividers, jaali) have aria-hidden="true"
- Gallery images have meaningful alt text
- Section landmarks with appropriate ARIA roles
- Focus indicators: 2px gold outline, visible on all interactive elements
- Skip-to-content link for keyboard users

### Semantic HTML

- Use semantic elements: main, section, nav, header, footer
- Each section wrapped in section element with aria-labelledby
- Headings follow proper hierarchy (h1 once, h2 per section)
- Event cards use article elements
- Form inputs have associated labels
- Language attribute: lang="en" with lang="hi" on Hindi text spans

