## RSVP FORM SPECIFICATION

### Fields

| Field | Type | Required | Validation | Full Name | Text input | Yes | Min 2 chars, max 100 |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Phone Number | Tel input | Yes | 10-digit Indian mobile format | Number of Guests | Number stepper | Yes | 1-10, default 1 |
| Attending Events | Multi-select checkboxes | Yes (min 1) | All events listed, all checked by default | Blessings/Message | Textarea | No | Max 500 chars, gold char counter |

### Form Behavior

- Submit triggers gold confetti burst (canvas-confetti library)
- Success state: form replaced with "Thank you" message + gold checkmark animation
- Error state: inline validation, gold-tinted error messages below fields
- Double-submit prevention: button disabled after first click
- Data stored in Google Sheets or Supabase (simple, no auth needed)
- No login required. No email verification.

### Form Styling

- Input fields: transparent bg, 1px `#C9A96E` 40% border, cream text
- Focus: border brightens to `#C9A96E` 100%, subtle gold glow
- Labels: Inter 500, 14px, `#D4CFC5`
- Placeholder text: `#8B7340` at 50%
- Checkbox: custom gold checkmark on midnight bg
- All inputs have 48px min height for touch

